products.name: SureFlap Microchip Pet Door Medium/Large Cat & Small Dog White
products.description:
The SureFlap Microchip Pet Door is an easy to program outdoor access solution, designed with your pet's safety in mind. It recognises your pet's existing microchip or the Sure Petcare RFID Collar Tag (1 included) to exclusively open for them, whilst preventing other animals from entering your home. The selective entry provides your pets with increased security against other animals and helps reduce the risk of territorial stress and scent marking. Using the integrated LCD display, you can easily monitor battery levels, set your pets' entry permissions and a curfew to automatically lock the pet door at a specific time (i.e.overnight).

With an opening size of 178mm (W) x 170mm (H), the Microchip Pet Door is suitable for large cats and small dogs. The exterior of the pet door measures 262mm (W) x 281mm (H), with a tunnel length of 70mm (D). The SureFlap Microchip Pet Door can be installed in doors, windows, and walls. For fitting into doors or walls, a hole size of 207mm (W) x 234mm (H) is required. For wall installations, the tunnel length is 70mm (D) and the SureFlap Microchip Pet Door Tunnel Extender (sold separately) may be required for thicker walls. When mounting in glass, a circular hole with a diameter of 300mm should be cut. The SureFlap Microchip Pet Door Mounting Adapter (sold separately) is needed to mount the pet door and cover any remaining space. It allows mounting into holes with a diameter of 300mm (min) to 320mm (max).

With a clean and minimalist design that doesn't require a mains connection and available in white and brown, the SureFlap Microchip Pet Door suits many homes and easily blends in with most home decor. With enough memory space for up to 32 pet IDs, the Microchip Pet Door is ideal for homes with multiple pets.

Battery powered (4 x C, not included) with up to 12 months battery life and a "battery low" indicator LED.Reads all common microchip formats (9, 10 and 15 digits) and the Sure Petcare RFID Collar Tag. 3 years warranty.
promotionName: Online Only Save 20% On Selected Sureflap Dog & Cat Accessories
products.fullItemName: SureFlap Microchip Pet Door for Medium/Large Cat & Small Dog White

Lock and unlock your Pet Door Connect remotely, check battery levels, set and change a curfew time, and be notified when your pets leave or enter the home.

With an opening size of 178mm (W) x 170mm (H), the Microchip Pet Door Connect is suitable for large cats and small dogs. The exterior of the pet door measures 262mm (W) x 281mm (H), with a tunnel length of 70mm (D). The SureFlap Microchip Pet Door Connect can be installed in doors, windows, and walls. For fitting into doors or walls, a hole size of 207mm (W) x 234mm (H) is required. For wall installations, the tunnel length is 70mm (D) and the SureFlap Microchip Cat Flap Tunnel Extender (sold separately) may be required for thicker walls. When mounting in glass, a circular hole with a diameter of 300mm should be cut. The SureFlap Microchip Pet Door Mounting Adapter (sold separately) is needed to mount the pet door and cover any remaining space. It allows mounting into holes with a diameter of 300mm (min) to 320mm (max).

With a clean and minimalist design and cable free, the SureFlap Microchip Pet Door Connect suits many homes and easily blends in with most home decor. With enough memory space for up to 32 pet ID, this pet door model is ideal for homes with multiple pets.

Battery powered (4 x AA, not included) with up to 6 months battery life and a "battery low" indicator LED. Reads all common microchip formats (9, 10 and 15 digits) and the Sure Petcare RFID Collar Tag. 3 years warranty.

products.name: BIOGANCE Biospotix Flea & Tick Repellent Small Dog Spot On
products.description: On contrary to chemical products with neurotoxic effects on insects, Biospotix has a mechanical approach and acts on contact with fleas and ticks. Based on Geraniol, Biospotix active ingredients dehydrate the Chitin (The chitin is the main component of the cell walls, the exoskeletons of insects and arthropods)* and block the insect's respiratory system. Parasites are then repelled by smothering and dehydration. The gaseous phase of Geraniol does also help to dehydrate eggs and larvae giving Biospotix excellent ovicidal and larvicidal properties.  Biospotix spot on is an effective solution to help protect your dog from fleas and ticks. Made in France.
